Interface IPersistentList<E>

Type Parameters:
E - Payload inside the Queue
All Known Implementing Classes:
ConcurrentPersistentList
public interface IPersistentList<E>

A concurrent queue where every element in the queue can be persisted into a persistent storage.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Dirk Müller (d.mueller@homelabs.de)
See Also:
IPersistentList}, ConcurrentPersistentList}, ConcurrentPersistentListNode}, IConcurrentPersistentListDao}
